             * @see https://apidocs.bithumb.com/v1.2.0/reference/%EA%B1%B0%EB%9E%98-%EC%A3%BC%EB%AC%B8%EB%82%B4%EC%97%AD-%EC%A1%B0%ED%9A%8C
             *
